data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The picture shows that there are some breathtaking architectures, which are probably made in the 1900s. Besides, as we can see from the picture, these buildings are made of stones, concrete and wood, which embody a kind of construction style in some foreign countries. There is a bridge, which is made of steel, in the middle of these two buildings so residents can easily arrive at their destinations with the help of this bridge. Finally, because of the color of the sky, we can also see that this photograph is taken in the morning. I do like this beautiful scenery.
